INSERT INTO workflow_schedules (workflow_id, user_id, config, next_run_at, enabled)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, true)
            ON CONFLICT (workflow_id)
            DO UPDATE SET
                config = EXCLUDED.config,
                next_run_at = EXCLUDED.next_run_at,
                enabled = EXCLUDED.enabled,
                updated_at = now()
